  "title": "Genshin Instruments",
  "description": "A mod that adds Genshin Impact's set of instruments into Minecraft!",
  "body": "<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/Z2BN6Y6/banner.png\" alt=\"Mod Banner - Genshin Instruments\" width=\"1000\" border=\"0\" /></p><center>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Add Genshin Impact's set of instruments to your own Minecraft experience, and play your favorite songs with the familiar keybindings!</h2></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Looking for <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/evenmoreinstruments\">even more instruments</a>? 👀<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">(New to playing? Check out <a title=\"How To Master the Genshin Lyre\" href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/blog/how-to-master-the-lyre-genshin-instruments-mod/\">this neat tutorial</a>)</span></p></center>\n<!--<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Join the Development Livestream!</strong></h1>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/YOqkeE_30Ik?wmode=transparent\" width=\"638\" height=\"358\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p><hr/>-->\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/_m7oIwfqpPI\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n  <br/>\n    <br/>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Full MIDI Support!</h1>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WaCIP4lWEzk\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/7PKk7qorFTk\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/IMJbt353j9o\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\">This mod adds the following instruments to the game:</span></span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Windsong Lyre</strong> [Stereo support]</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Floral Zither</strong> [Old &amp; New]</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Vintage Lyre</strong> [Normalization support]</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Arataki's Great and Glorious Drum</strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Nightwind Horn</strong> [Sustainable]</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Instrument re-textures done by the awesome Gen (<a href=\"https://github.com/StavWasPlayZ/Genshin-Instruments/issues/9\">#9</a>)! Check out their stuff, and show your support 😋<br />\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/GenMode\">Modrinth</a> | <a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/member/gen/\">PlanetMinecraft</a> | <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/GenMedia\">Patreon</a> | <a title=\"@DatapackGen\" href=\"https://twitter.com/DatapackGen\">Twitter</a></span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 14px;\"><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Support for:</span></span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Custom pitch on each instrument</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Adjustable transposition with Left/Right shift (as set by your keybinds)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Several sets of note labels (Keyboard labels match your language &amp; layout)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Multiplayer and shared instrument screens!</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>⚠️ IMPORTANT ⚠️: The Mod Author has Retired the project</strong></h2>\n<p>Watch the video below to learn more:</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/TUzdklT4vcs?wmode=transparent\" width=\"638\" height=\"358\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>  \n<h1>Content Spotlight</h1>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/1CVVqa2BHVE\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/bCLnB21RSj4\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/lzwnBKp6Pg0\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Gvs3MRvkJR4\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>(The video above was made possible through the <a href=\"https://github.com/k5md/M2KB\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">M2KB</a> project)</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr /><center>\n<p><h3><strong>Are you a content creator? Lyre player?</strong></h3></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Reach out to me in <a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/private-messages/send?recipient=stavwasplays\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">CurseForge PMs</a> to have your video showcased <strong>here</strong>!</span></p>\n</center><hr />\n<h2><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Recipes</strong></span></h2>\n<p><strong>Windsong Lyre<br></strong></p>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fMDz9ul.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"190\"></strong></p>\n<p><strong>Vintage Lyre</strong></p>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Dtbc6lk.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"190\"></strong></p>\n<p><strong>Floral Zither</strong></p>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cMR8lkA.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"190\"></strong></p>\n<p><strong>Arataki's Great and Glorious Drum</strong></p>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/165Cjnf.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"190\"></strong></p>\n<p><strong>Nightwind Horn<br></strong></p>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bY07PUc.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"190\"></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><b>THIS PROJECT IS NOT AFFILIATED WITH NEITHER HOYOVERSE NOR GENSHIN IMPACT.</b></span><br>\nAll audio assets and design elements belong to said company.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br />What started as a small, learning test project, has made its way to be my first ever published creation. I'm very thrilled and excited to be able to share something with the community, as both an average Minecraft and Genshin enjoyer :^)</p>",
